      class  ASTUserDefinedFunction
      In the org.openntf.formula engine, you can define own functions:

      Example: Define the function "myFunc" with 1-2 parametes:
      @function( @myfunc( a; b:=3) ) = @Left(a,b+1);

      Calling @myfunc( "Hello" ) will return "Hell" ( the same as @Left("Hello";4) )
